      <scopecontent>
         <head>Scope and Content Information</head>
         <p>This addition to the papers of former diplomat R. Smith
         Simpson (1906- ) contains ca. 225 items (3 Hollinger boxes),
         1918-1991, consisting of Christmas letters, bound printed
         material concerning the activities and writings of Simpson, an
         oral history interview with Simpson, and committee records,
         including newsletters, memoranda, and minutes of the Committee
         for the Study of Diplomacy.</p>
      </scopecontent>
